Run these one by one in PowerShell:
Step 1 — Create a fresh conda environment (recommended over .venv)
powershell
conda create -n kyc python=3.10 -y
Step 2 — Activate it
powershell
conda activate kyc
Step 3 — Install everything cleanly
powershellpip install opencv-python numpy==1.26.4 pandas==2.0.0 matplotlib jupyter ipykernel tqdm streamlit
Step 4 — Register it as a Jupyter kernel so notebooks work
powershellpython -m ipykernel install --user --name kyc --display-name "Python (kyc)"
Step 5 — Run the pipeline
powershellcd C:\kyc-document-quality
python src/pipeline.py